  <source>Sha’ar Menashe Mental Health Center</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Online consulatations through videoconference in the field of psychiatry given to general
      practitioners will reduce costs of medical treatment and improve service.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      CLINICAL STATE, SATISFACTION AND COST EFFECTIVENESS WILL BE CHECKED DURING 1 YEAR OF ONLINE
      VIDEO CONFERENCE CONSULTATION TO GENERAL PRACTITIONERS. BPRS, HAMILTON ANXIETY AND DEPRESSION
      AND CGI SCALES WILL BE COMPLETED.COSTS OF MEDICATIONS, NUMBER OF VISITS, LAB AND OTHER
      EXAMINATIONS, HOSPITALIZATIONS, MISSING WORKING DAYS WILL BE EVALUATED.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
